        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks JVC for his biography [of CD].</p> 
<p>Has almost finished first proofs of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p>  
<p>Has difficulty in answering JVC’s queries about dogs because of differences in German names and breeds. Refers him to A. E. Brehm’s <hi rend="italic">Illustrirtes Thierleben</hi> [1868] and, on pigeons, to Gottlob Neumeister’s book [<hi rend="italic">Das Ganze der Taubenzucht</hi> (1837)].</p> 
            <p>Hopes JVC is not discouraged by first volume. Thinks second will be more interesting.</p>
        </abstract>
